        <div class="col-md-12" id="browser">
            <h2 class="text-left">
                <strong>
                    Dukungan Browser
                </strong>
            </h2>
            <h4>
                Untuk mengetahui versi browser:
            </h4>
            <span>
                <strong>
                    Google Chrome
                </strong>
            </span>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    Klik menu setting pada browser chrome, pada bagian pojok kanan atas
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="dist/images/settings/chrome_set.png" alt="Setting"/>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Kemudian pilih "Help" dan pilih "About Google Chrome"
                    <img class="img-responsive" style="padding-top: 10px; display: inline-block;" src="dist/images/settings/chrome_set_about.png" alt="Setting"/>
                </li>
            </ol>
            <span>
                <strong>
                    Mozilla Firefox
                </strong>
            </span>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    Klik menu setting pada browser firefox, pada bagian pojok kanan atas
                    <img class="img-responsive" src="dist/images/settings/firefox_set.png" alt="Setting"/>
                </li>
                <li>
                    Kemudian pilih "Help" dan pilih "About Mozilla Firefox"
                    <img class="img-responsive" style="padding-top: 10px; display: inline-block;" src="dist/images/settings/firefox_set_help.png" alt="Setting"/>
                    <img class="img-responsive" style="padding-top: 10px; display: inline-block;" src="dist/images/settings/firefox_set_about.png" alt="Setting"/>
                </li>
            </ol>            
            <h4>
                Daftar versi browser yang didukung
            </h4>
            <ol>
                <li>
                    Google Chrome (Windows, Mac, Linux) versi 20 keatas
                </li>
                <li>
                    Mozilla Firefox (Windows, Mac, Linux) versi 10 keatas
                </li>
                <li>
                    Microsoft Internet Explorer (Windows 7, Windows 8, Windows RT, Windows Phone 8) versi 10 keatas
                </li>
                <li>
                    Desktop Safari (Windows and Mac), direkomendasikan versi 5.1 atau keatas
                </li>
                <li>
                    Mobile Safari di perangkat iOS (iPhone, iPad, iPod Touch), direkomendasikan versi 5.1 atau keatas
                </li>
                <li>
                    Android Default Browsers, OS yang direkomendasikan Android versi 4.0 keatas
                </li>
            </ol>
